description._content: Description: View in the middle of March of 1930, of the Northern slope of Madari from the pass above Saranti, Adelphi Forest,Elevation about 4,500 feet. Location: Cyprus Date: March 1930 Description: View in April, 1930 (Mavra Dassi) "Black Forest" above and East of Kannavia, Adelphi Forest, middle Elvation about 2,800 feet. Location: Cyprus Date: April 1930 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/698 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown. We have attempted to provide place information for the images automatically but our software may not have found the correct location.
